{"tid":108533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸客團遊南非遇劫　3人在飯店大廳挨槍濺血","createTime":"2017-02-05T10:30:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-05T14:10:53.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7ace64616bfa129402b7b74a153a2cdb1ea9f969","tid":108533,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T10:30:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170205/420_be6370d5fcd2d11f6eff5c43b18436cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170205%2F420_be6370d5fcd2d11f6eff5c43b18436cf.jpg&h=5b100466&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n事發在約翰尼斯堡機場的假日飯店。翻攝Google地圖 <br />\n<br />\n又傳陸客在海外遭劫，廣西省柳州市一個旅行社，上月30日春節期間組團到南非觀光，於當地時間2月4日晚間23時左右，下榻南非約翰尼斯堡機場附近的HOLIDAY INN JOHANNESBURG AIRPORT飯店，豈料團員在飯店櫃台附近聊天時，突然有劫匪闖入，搶奪財物。 <br />\n<br />\n他們與劫匪周旋時，對方持工業用的砂槍，連發數槍，將3人射傷，其中包括一對母女，3人當場血流如注，其中1人被射中眉心，情況最嚴重，已進行手術，其他2人都脫離險境。 <br />\n<br />\n（大陸中心／綜合外電報導） <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170205/420_cc4fb1352c34c3e70f9800144b25fb9d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170205%2F420_cc4fb1352c34c3e70f9800144b25fb9d.jpg&h=591f081e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170205/420_db477efb3131ad8df7d963e5d1d1e8b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170205%2F420_db477efb3131ad8df7d963e5d1d1e8b2.jpg&h=9ff39437&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20170205/420_f18887f0d05fdb35de07cffb9afacf7b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20170205%2F420_f18887f0d05fdb35de07cffb9afacf7b.jpg&h=1262206d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ad0c5a4d9fda348ad70c290bdbcb2ff1dbce1ab0","tid":108533,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T10:31:49.000Z","msg":"砂槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1103180a6f079fcf37951e34bcd7e4db77f7c11f","tid":108533,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T10:34:11.000Z","msg":"又玩飛鏢？"},{"pid":"27d510eced926105b71bb57ee60451cee436b625","tid":108533,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T10:57:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0cddf5b6408c20c6dfa3aa8ab6f541bdc6964d2","tid":108533,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:00:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be30212ae3db459382e6e79a662bba263dbe84e1","tid":108533,"uid":9292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:07:23.000Z","msg":"打中眉心都唔死？"},{"pid":"066bea2c082e6213609c1f8251de9a88b33bc1e7","tid":108533,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-05T14:10:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打中眉心都唔死？</blockquote><br />\n食埋食埋咁多化學原素先頂到陣咋，你估好易呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}